<br>
Except of course when someone says we are uber, then we get compared to just about every class (always by people who never played a Skald in the first place)<br>
<br>
We are like Minstrels, because of speed, we are like Paladins because of chants, we are like Champs due to DDs, etc, etc.  <br>
It's impossible to pin us down.<br>
<br>
Rosey<br>
<br>
