<br>
We're a minstrel with ghetto mid 2h, no stealth, and our music lines are a tad different.<br>
<br>
-dd's =Minstrels are 25% faster than ours<br>
-Mez =Minstrels have a long duration single target that can be cast on the run and a ghetto ae mez<br>
-snare =Minstrels have insta 9s stun on a really short timer<br>
-Dmg add =Minstrels ablative (ablative helps everybody, dmg add helps only melees in it's very short range)<br>
-Speed =Minstrels have to use an instrument<br>
-Resist chants = Minstrels don't really have anything like this unless you count ablative again, not that anybody would really want the resist chants.<br>
-Rest song =Minstrels have to use an instrument<br>
-Specable parry/evade1 =Evade II, medium shield, dodger, higher dex/qui<br>
<br>
So if you give a minstrel a mid 2h weapon, take away power regen, charm, remove mez, confusion, stealth, climb walls and then make their remaining spells slightly less useful you have a skald.   <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#d1c2a2><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub36.ezboard.com/bteamskald.showUserPublicProfile?gid=talozshado>Taloz Shado</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br>  Posts: 1<br> <font color=#ff0000>(3/6/03 1:52:32 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub36.ezboard.com/fteamskaldfrm1.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=527.topic&index=5>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> minstrels</span><hr size=1> Minstrels got some tweaks recently, and do seem to be overall a stronger class than skalds.  But there are some more differences.<br>
<br>
Minstrels only get small shields, and dealing with instruments is pretty crappy, extra buttons, and you can't switch back and forth between more than one instrument easily.  There are small shields with medium looking skins though that can confuse things.<br>
<br>
Also, skalds have protect for PvE while minstrels get confuse, protect is the better of the two imo, but both are fairly minor overall.<br>
<br>
Power song - Drum<br>
Healing song - Lute<br>
Speed song - Drum<br>
Mez - Flute<br>
<br>
And the stun is only 700 range like the DD's, while snare is 1500 range. <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#efe0c0><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub36.ezboard.com/bteamskald.showUserPublicProfile?gid=albron>Albron</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Team Skald Fervent</span><br>  Posts: 104<br> <font color=#ff0000>(3/6/03 7:50:44 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub36.ezboard.com/fteamskaldfrm1.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=527.topic&index=6>Reply</a>   <BR><img src=http://www.tyrantsonline.com/albron.gif WIDTH=60 HEIGHT=60></td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: minstrels</span><hr size=1> Unless they changed it and I missed the patch notes minstrels get Medium shields.  However, yeah instruments suck.<br>
